data.description: Beautiful 4 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath with large, fenced backyard! Freshly painted walls, beautiful hardwood floors, stunning grey cabinets and a separate dining room. All bedrooms and the laundry room are upstairs. The gorgeous master bedroom has its own private balcony! Enjoy the walk-in closets. End your day outside on the large deck! This welcoming home is waiting for you!
